{"tid":402444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒！城巴真係應該執撚左佢！！！","createTime":"2017-09-16T12:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T14:02:43.000Z","uid":101750,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"960e9f821801f8c15bdbdf484d0003721bc738d2","tid":402444,"uid":101750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:27:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我企左係條街度等左45分鐘都未撚有車！！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都知我戇鳩嫁啦  但等左咁耐又真係無理由唔繼續等嫁嘛<br />\n<br />\n仲要今日真係好撚柒鳩熱！<br />\n<br />\n企撚到個人都出撚晒汗<br />\n<br />\n人地九巴都有個check 到站既APP <br />\n<br />\n城巴個等車時間表長期撚鳩人 要人估幾時有車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係執撚左佢啦屌！！！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7100a3c872a5d473ba5665b3b93842b8167db24","tid":402444,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:29:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾app"},{"pid":"d2e7efda02531820910d38feb30d8bff30a707b8","tid":402444,"uid":101750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"如果搭地鐵真係一早返撚左屋企喇屌！ ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32566a967946f0463956d21e2b40e58503915220","tid":402444,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果搭地鐵真係一早返撚左屋企喇屌！ ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇錯九巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過其實九巴個app都好撚伏<br />\n岩岩就係等太耐轉左地鐵"},{"pid":"f83aff9b05646ccb5a394a4a59acfff81a4c957b","tid":402444,"uid":101750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾app</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然有時都唔準 <br />\n<br />\n但至少我未試過戇鳩鳩等半個鐘以上<br />\n<br />\n好撚過城巴連app 都冇 呃鳩人等車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec5e0625640e82e361f7973bbc428bccea84fe4","tid":402444,"uid":1621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得九巴個app幾準"},{"pid":"eff54d052166132dd39e534dab1ebb36fc1e4282","tid":402444,"uid":101750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得九巴個app幾準</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係算係咁 至少可以預返時間趕巴士"},{"pid":"024b72c7b27744dbe3263b3679a490ce210d4b3e","tid":402444,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:13:40.000Z","msg":"有得揀我都唔想搭城巴，夏天企喺到賭博咁"},{"pid":"53a3463250e7feb903a53978ccd9b5b249543413","tid":402444,"uid":2277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"搭開城巴過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又多車又準時又快"},{"pid":"b90bef8cf592201c0c0da69643774b1d349e553b","tid":402444,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:16:04.000Z","msg":"邊條線先"},{"pid":"b79d92d969ccb1d8092a31b25f4dd2f6656b23fc","tid":402444,"uid":101750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有得揀我都唔想搭城巴，夏天企喺到賭博咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n形容得好貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又驚miss左班車企係馬路邊 <br />\n其他所車經過D廢氣湧出來 <br />\n真係熱撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n今日真係衰戇鳩 唔應該搭城巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b933c70c28a34ac577f3c6cdca5a9e1321020398","tid":402444,"uid":101750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭開城巴過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又多車又準時又快</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過海點同<br />\n如果港島線都delay 真係比人日日屌撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec6fb1f1998aa9d08739751f14535e137059f99","tid":402444,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得九巴個app幾準</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係算係咁 至少可以預返時間趕巴士</blockquote><br />\n九巴個app準就唔洗比人屌老母<br />\n<br />\n成日有鬼車，10分鐘慢慢等到2分鐘，再快將到達，之後再變返10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274e1fe79d7a54f64dbd0d7902c60417d4639af8","tid":402444,"uid":101750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得九巴個app幾準</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係算係咁 至少可以預返時間趕巴士</blockquote><br />\n九巴個app準就唔洗比人屌老母<br />\n<br />\n成日有鬼車，10分鐘慢慢等到2分鐘，再快將到達，之後再變返10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 但有得預時間好過冇得預時間 等半個鐘以上真係好撚無奈 唔知繼唔繼續等好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07996816e6f23c5e962d37d159f0dbb35c5f6319","tid":402444,"uid":107334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"九巴app 我搭開果啲都幾準<br />\n<br />\n算係咁啦，之前半版廣告比人屌到反皮，而且真係cut 到5分1"}]}